Package org.agreement_technologies.agents

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AgentListener
    AgentListener is the interface that all planning agents must implement.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GUIBoot
    GUIBoot is the class that implements the graphical interface that allow to launch the planning agents and monitorize the search process.
    GUIdisRPG
    Graphical interface to show the disRPG data (distributed relaxed planning graph).
    GUILandmarks
    GUILandmarks is the class that shows the landmark graph graphically.
    GUIPlanningAgent
    GUIPlanningAgent is the graphical interface for a planning agent.
    GUISearchTree
    GUISearchTree is a graphic form that shows the search tree.
    GUITrace
    GUITrace is a graphical interface to show trace data of a planning agent.
    MAPboot
    MAPboot is the main class of this project (FMAP).
    PlanningAgent
    PlanningAgent represents a planning agent.
    PlanningAlgorithm
    PlanningAlgorithm class implements the distributed planning protocol.
